Company Overview of UBILITE Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
UBILITE Inc. designs, manufactures, and markets semiconductors for wireless connectivity products. It offers ultra low power, disposable and wearable wireless local area networks that are used in sensing and controlling consumer and enterprise applications. The company was founded in 2014 and is headquartered in Carlsbad, California.


